   Schema: Risk_arm  Entity: Risk_evaluation  
   <express_ref linkend="risk:arm:Risk_arm.Risk_evaluation"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Risk_arm.Risk_evaluation">
A <b>Risk_evaluation</b> is a type of Activity that evalutes the risk with respect to the
<express_ref linkend="risk:arm:Risk_arm.Risk_evaluation_criteria"/> as part of the <express_ref linkend="risk:arm:Risk_arm.Risk_assessment"/>
to determine the significance of the <express_ref linkend="risk_definition:arm:Risk_definition_arm.Risk"/>.
<note><express_ref linkend="risk:arm:Risk_arm.Risk_evaluation"/> may be used to assist in the acceptance or treatment decision.</note>
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Risk_arm  Entity: Risk_evaluation_criteria  
   <express_ref linkend="risk:arm:Risk_arm.Risk_evaluation_criteria"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Risk_arm.Risk_evaluation_criteria">
A <b>Risk_evaluation_criteria</b> is a type of 
<express_ref linkend="activity:arm:Activity_arm.Applied_activity_assignment"/>
that defines the criterias for a specific <express_ref linkend="risk:arm:Risk_arm.Risk_evaluation"/>
</ext_description>
<!-- 
